# smartutils

A lightweight Python utility library for string and math operations.

## Modules

### string_utils
- reverse_string(text)
- count_vowels(text)
- is_palindrome(text)
- capitalize_words(text)

### math_utils
- add(a, b)
- subtract(a, b)
- factorial(n)
- is_prime(n)
